
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These are the formulas I used to calculate the different KPI: KPI CY Less PY, KPI Profit Avg, KPI Sales Avg |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=======================================================

KPI CY Less PY

Formula

IF SUM([CY Sales])< SUM([PY Sales ]) THEN 'â¬¤'
ELSE''
END

=======================================================

KPI Profit Avg 

Formula

IF SUM([CY Profit])>WINDOW_AVG(SUM([CY Profit]))
THEN'above'
ELSE'below'
END

=======================================================

KPI Sales Avg

Formula

IF SUM([CY Sales])>WINDOW_AVG(SUM([CY Sales]))
THEN'above'
ELSE'below'
END

=======================================================
